# CARDORA Apple App Review

**Status:** Planned

---

# Overview

This document tracks the requirements for submitting CARDORA to the Apple App Store.

Its purpose is to ensure that the application complies with Apple's App Review Guidelines before public release.

---

# General Requirements

Before submission, verify that:

* The application launches successfully.
* No crashes occur during normal use.
* The user interface is responsive.
* Performance is stable across supported devices.

---

# Authentication

Supported authentication methods:

* Email Sign In
* Google Sign-In
* Sign in with Apple (when required by Apple)

Authentication should function correctly on all supported devices.

---

# Permissions

Verify the following permissions:

* Camera
* Photo Library
* Internet Access

Only request permissions when required by the application.

---

# Purchases

Verify:

* Founder purchase
* Early Supporter purchase
* Pro Subscription
* Restore Purchases
* Membership synchronization

---

# Privacy

Before submission:

* Privacy Policy published
* Account Deletion available
* Privacy Labels completed
* App Privacy information verified

---

# Store Listing

Verify:

* App Name
* Subtitle
* Description
* Keywords
* Screenshots
* App Icon

---

# Compatibility

Confirm compatibility with:

* iPhone
* iPad (if supported)
* Latest iOS version
* Previous supported iOS versions

---

# Compliance

Verify compliance with:

* App Store Review Guidelines
* Human Interface Guidelines
* Privacy requirements
* Legal requirements

---

# Submission Checklist

* [ ] Application tested
* [ ] Store Listing completed
* [ ] Privacy information completed
* [ ] Purchases verified
* [ ] No critical bugs
* [ ] Submitted for Review
* [ ] Approved by Apple

